{"tid":1709851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍翔道混凝土車涉撞車後泥漿瀉地 要封路清理","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T04:09:12.000Z","uid":102466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e762f0b4e76b07118151fb48cb7bef356ce2d5","tid":1709851,"uid":102466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"下午約3時，一輛重型貨車與運載混凝土車，在黃大仙龍翔道往觀塘方向近天馬苑發生碰撞，事件中無人受傷，但混凝土車部份泥漿瀉落路面，使部份行車綫要封閉清理，現場嚴重擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署宣佈，因交通意外，龍翔道往觀塘方向近天馬苑的部份行車綫現已封閉。駕駛人士只可使用餘下行車綫行車。至下午5時車龍的龍尾延至蘇屋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfWJvhw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfWJvhw.jpg&h=7f136c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2ssWXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2ssWXx.jpg&h=d5df3bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望唔好再發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到咁點返工阿"},{"pid":"62301c3c7fe14056e1da29e160f412862e880300","tid":1709851,"uid":9450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"屈機"}]}